		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Tag <code>T3E</code>: Ontologies</h1>
		Work using knowledge graphs, ontologies, or semantic web representations for language engineering tasks: semantic integration, conceptual alignment, data inference, or reasoning over language artefacts with ontology-based formalisms. If the core contribution is requirements capture, <a href="t5a.html">T5A</a> Requirements can be primary.
